===Etymology===
Fanciful extension of [[sesquippedalophobia|sesqui(p)pedalophobia]] with [[monstrum]] "monster" and a truncated form of [[hippopotamus]], intended to exaggerate the length of the word itself and the idea of the size of the words being feared. The word consists of 36 letters.

===Noun===
'''hippopotomonstrosesquippedaliophobia''' (''[[uncountable]]'')
#Fear of long words.

